@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Cancelled : submit
Cancelled --> Created : review
Created --> Rejected : approve
Rejected --> Completed : update
Rejected : entry / log route
Completed --> Draft : approve
Completed : entry / log route
Completed --> Rejected : revert
Draft --> [*]
@enduml